!!! PLEASE USE FONT PACKAGES PROVIDED BY YOUR DISTRIBUTION IF AVAILABLE!!!	

For all other cases:

To make the font system wide available, do the following steps as root or 
with sudo:
  * mkdir /usr/share/fonts/truetype/ukai
  * cp *.ttc fonts.* /usr/share/fonts/truetype/ukai
  * cp *.conf /etc/fonts/conf.avail/
  * cd /etc/fonts/conf.d
  * ln -s ../conf.avail/*-ttf-arphic-ukai-*.conf .
  * fc-cache -fv
  * xset fp rehash
